logy and policy initiatives.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 10. Jan 2022) 0aSoil conservation. 0aSoil erosionxClimatic factors. 0aSoil erosion. 7aNATURE / Natural Resources.2bisacsh1 aCohen, Kayla.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311073923740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300263107423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300263107/original  a978-3-11-073923-7  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles